System Requirements
-------------------
Same requirements as the OJS 2.3.6 core.
Additionally PHP 5 >= 5.0.1, PHP Soap, and PHP OpenSSL extension modules.

Installation
------------
To install the plugin either:
 - copy the plugin tar.gz file to your OJS/plugins/generic directory
 - to unzip the plugin inside the plugins/generic directory:
    $ tar xvzf vgWort-1.0.tar.gz 
 - from your OJS directory execute :
    $ php tools/upgrade.php upgrade
 - enable the plugin by going to:  Home > User > Journal Management > Plugin Management > Generic Plugins and selecting "ENABLE" under "VG Wort"

